PANDORA

- splash screen simply states what the site does, prompts user for an artist, genre or composer
	- sleek background
	- header lets you register, login, or get help
	- company, music, and pandora resource links at the bottom

- entering critera immediately brings you to the player, layered on top of the screen (separate from the rest)
	- header has a nav bar which controls the player
	- has album art and previous songs in the middle
	- designed to look like a media player app
	- bottom has lyrics (if available), artist bio, and similar artists, publish, share, or buy track
	- color scheme allows the player and links to stand out
